com.spotify.zoltar.loaders

Interface Preloader<M extends Model<?>>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - Model instance type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    ModelLoader<M>
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface Preloader<M extends Model<?>>
extends ModelLoader<M>
    Preloader is model loader that calls ModelLoader.get() allowing model preloading.
